item.title: This Hotel Room Suite 21 Phlocking
item.description: The annual two day fundraiser for the St. MinneSomePlace Parrot Head Club featuring entertainment by Jambo Joe Bones, Jim Hoehn, Mary Cutrufello, and The Compass Rose Band.
